{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"annotation","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation object to remove. This object must conform"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Removing an annotation object dissociates it from the map view entirely,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"preventing it from being displayed on the map. Thus you would typically call","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this method only when you want to hide or delete a given annotation.","type":"text"}]}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"role":"symbol","title":"removeAnnotation:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)removeAnnotation:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"removeAnnotation:"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1820"},"symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:"]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected."}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/removeAnnotation:":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removeAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/removeAnnotation:","abstract":[{"text":"Removes an annotation from the map view, deselecting it if it is selected.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/removeannotation:","title":"removeAnnotation:","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"title":"MLNMapView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"type":"topic"}}}